OL,4,Ckilling wife 'seen running shop in
OL,5,CIndia'
OL,7,FPankaj Lamba, Ms Brella's husband, was
OL,8,Frunning a store near Delhi, not far
OL,9,Ffrom his childhood home. Locals told
OL,10,Fus he kept his face covered, and he
OL,11,Fwas with a woman and a young child.
OL,13,FITV News has been told by his former
OL,14,Fteacher, Mr Sunil Saini, that he last
OL,15,Fsaw Pankaj there in April when he
OL,16,Fclosed the store, which is now an egg
OL,17,Fshop, because the police were closing
OL,18,Fin.
