OL,7,FHe said: "He contacted me again in
OL,8,FFebruary or March. Before leaving
OL,9,Ftown, he came to meet me and mentioned
OL,10,Fthat he had some items from a
OL,11,Frestaurant.
OL,13,F"He said, 'If you're planning to open
OL,14,Fa restaurant, you can use them - or if
OL,15,Fnot, you can try to sell them.' This
OL,16,Fconversation took place around the
OL,17,F10th or 11th of April this year."
