OL,12,FDetectives believe 24-year-old
OL,13,FHarshita Brella was killed by Lamba in
OL,14,FCorby, Northamptonshire, on the
OL,15,Fevening of 10 November 2024.
OL,17,FMs Brella was then found dead in a car
OL,18,Ffour days later in Ilford, east London
OL,19,F- almost 100 miles away.
