OL,7,FAn international manhunt was launched
OL,8,Ffor Lamba after the discovery of Ms
OL,9,FBrella's body, with police saying at
OL,10,Fthe time that he was thought to have
OL,11,Ffled the country.
OL,13,FHe was charged in his absence for his
OL,14,Fwife's murder and is also accused of
OL,15,Ftwo counts of rape, sexual assault,
OL,16,Fand controlling or coercive behaviour.
OL,18,FHer family believe that if officers
OL,19,Fhad acted properly, their daughter
OL,20,Fwould still be alive, and her killer
OL,21,Fwould not still be on the run.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
