OL,7,FHarshita's father, Satbir Singh, told
OL,8,FITV News: "We're nowhere close to
OL,9,Fgetting justice. There's no trace of
OL,10,Fhim, and the Delhi Police aren't
OL,11,Fsharing any updates. We're completely
OL,12,Fin the dark."
OL,14,FRemembering her late daughter, Sudesh
OL,15,FKumari said: "I just can't forget her.
OL,16,FI can't sleep at night. She comes to
OL,17,Fmy mind, but I don't even see her in
OL,18,Fmy dreams. I miss her day and night."
