OL,7,F"If guests came, she'd make tea and
OL,8,Fhot and cold food, everything. I miss
OL,9,Fher every moment.
OL,11,F"We didn't celebrate Diwali this year.
OL,12,FI couldn't celebrate without my
OL,13,Fdaughter. I miss her deeply; I miss
OL,14,Fher so much."
OL,16,FIn a press conference last week, the
OL,17,FIndian Government said it had no
OL,18,Fupdate on the case because of the
OL,19,Flegal issues involved.
