OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Indian Foreign
OL,8,FMinistry said: "I do not have an
OL,9,Fupdate on the Harshita Brella case,
OL,10,Fbut I understand this is a matter that
OL,11,Fhas legal implications and that the
OL,12,Fmatter is subjudice.
OL,14,F"I'll give you an update on this
OL,15,Fmatter as to where exactly we stand in
OL,16,Fterms of the co-operation between
OL,17,FIndia and the UK, as to what we have
OL,18,Fto do to take this matter forward from
OL,19,Fthe point of egalities and judicial
OL,20,Fproceedings."
