OL,7,FSonia Dabas, Harshita's sister, has
OL,8,Fcalled for the case to be passed to
OL,9,FIndia's federal investigation agency.
OL,11,FShe said: "Indian police are not doing
OL,12,Fanything, they are in silent mode,
OL,13,Fthey are sleeping. They don't know
OL,14,Fwhere is Pankaj."
OL,16,FITV News has spent the last year
OL,17,Fworking with Harshita's family to
OL,18,Festablish where Pankaj Lamba might be
OL,19,Fhiding.
