OL,7,F"The neighbouring shopkeepers told me
OL,8,Fhe would never come out in the
OL,9,Fsunlight, he was always wearing a
OL,10,Fmask. He was always in dim light. So
OL,11,Fobviously, he had in the back of his
OL,12,Fmind that somebody was watching him."
OL,14,FA report by the Independent Office for
OL,15,FPolice Complaints is due to be
OL,16,Freleased later this month,
OL,17,Finvestigating alleged failings in how
OL,18,FNorthamptonshire Police handled
OL,19,Fcomplaints made by Ms Brella about
OL,20,FPankaj Lamba in the weeks leading up
OL,21,Fto her death.
