OL,4,Ckilling wife 'seen running shop in
OL,5,CIndia'
OL,7,F"Twelve months ago, on November 14,
OL,8,F2024, a murder investigation was
OL,9,Flaunched after 24-year-old Harshita
OL,10,Fwas found dead in a vehicle in the
OL,11,FIlford area of London after being
OL,12,Freported missing from her home in
OL,13,FCorby, Northamptonshire. In March
OL,14,F2025, the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,15,Fdecided that 24-year-old Pankaj Lamba,
OL,16,FHarshita's husband, should be charged
OL,17,Fwith murder in relation to her death.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
