OL,3,CHarshita Brella: Fugitive accused of
OL,4,Ckilling wife 'seen running shop in
OL,5,CIndia'
OL,7,F"This is an exceptionally complex case
OL,8,Fand with criminal proceedings now
OL,9,Factive in the UK, we are unable to go
OL,10,Finto detail about the investigation at
OL,11,Fthis time. However, we can confirm
OL,12,Fthat the Indian authorities have been
OL,13,Fmade aware through the appropriate
OL,14,Fchannels of the charging decision.
OL,16,F"The investigation is very much
OL,17,Fongoing and we remain as determined as
OL,18,Fever to bring the person responsible
OL,19,Ffor Harshita's death to justice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
