OL,7,F"Once again, I would like to extend my
OL,8,Fdeepest condolences to Harshita's
OL,9,Ffamily, and we will continue to offer
OL,10,Fsupport as the investigation and our
OL,11,Fwork to secure justice for Harshita
OL,12,Fand her family continues."
OL,14,FITV News has contacted Delhi Police
OL,15,Ffor comment.
